      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To protect the Nation's law enforcement officers by regulating the sale of the Five-seveN pistol and its variants, testing handguns for capability to penetrate body armor, and regulating the manufacture, importation, sale, or purchase of such handguns by civilians.</title>
